description.narrative: The project development objective (PDO) is to support the Borrower to (i) reduce flooding in the catchment of the Colombo WaterBasin, and (ii) strengthen the capacity of local authorities in the Colombo Metropolitan Area (CMA) to rehabilitate, improve andmaintain local infrastructure and services through selected demonstration investments.
